\c 37
\s Amaphupho kaJosefa
\p
\v 1 UJakobe wasehlala elizweni uyise ayehlala kilo njengowezizwe\f + \fk njengowezizwe: \fl Heb. \fq ilizwe lokuhlala kukayise njengowezizwe.\f*, ilizwe leKhanani.
\v 2 Lezi zindaba zezizukulwana zikaJakobe\x + 2.4; 6.9.\x*. UJosefa\x + 30.24.\x*, eleminyaka elitshumi lesikhombisa, wayeselusa umhlambi labafowabo, wayengumfana, elamadodana kaBiliha, lamadodana kaZilipa, omkayise; uJosefa waseletha kuyise imibiko emibi ngabo\x + 1 Sam. 2.23,24.\x*.
\v 3 Njalo uIsrayeli wayemthanda uJosefa kulawo wonke amadodana akhe, ngoba wayeyindodana yobudala kuye\x + 44.20.\x*; wamenzela isigqoko esilemibalabala\f + \fk esilemibalabala: \fl kumbe, \fq esiyiziqaziqa.\f*.
\v 4 Kwathi abafowabo sebebonile ukuthi uyise uyamthanda kulabo bonke abafowabo, bamzonda, babengelakukhuluma kuye ngokuthula.
\p
\v 5 UJosefa wasephupha iphupho, wa\add l\add*azisa abafowabo; ngakho baqhubeka bemzonda kakhulu.
\v 6 Wasesithi kibo: Ake lizwe leliphupho engiliphuphileyo.
\v 7 Khangelani-ke, besibopha izithungo phakathi kwensimu, njalo khangelani, isithungo sami sema saqonda futhi, khangelani-ke, izithungo zenu zazingelezela, zasikhothamela isithungo sami\x + 42.6,9; 43.26; 44.14.\x*.
\v 8 Abafowabo basebesithi kuye: Kanti ukubusa uzasibusa, ukulawula uzasilawula yini? Ngakho baqhubeka bemzonda kakhulu, ngenxa yamaphupho akhe langenxa yamazwi akhe.
\p
\v 9 Wasebuya futhi waphupha elinye iphupho, walilandisela abafowabo, wathi: Khangelani, ngiphuphe futhi iphupho; khangelani-ke, ilanga lenyanga lenkanyezi ezilitshumi lanye zingikhothamela.
\v 10 Waselandisela uyise labafowabo. Uyise wasemsola wathi kuye: Liyini leliphupho oliphuphileyo? Ukuza sizakuza, mina lonyoko\x + 35.18.\x* labafowenu, sikhothamele emhlabathini phambi kwakho yini?
\v 11 Abafowabo-ke baba lomona ngaye\x + Seb. 7.9.\x*, kodwa uyise waligcina lelilizwi\x + Dan. 7.28. Luka 2.19,51.\x*.
\s Ukuthengiswa kukaJosefa
\p
\v 12 Abafowabo basebehamba ukulagisa umhlambi kayise eShekema\x + 33.18.\x*.
\v 13 UIsrayeli wasesithi kuJosefa: Abafowenu kabalagisi eShekema yini? Woza, ngikuthume kibo. Wasesithi kuye: Khangela, ngi\add lapha\add*.
\v 14 Wasesithi kuye: Hamba-ke, ubone ukuthi baphila kuhle\f + \fk baphila kuhle: \fl Heb. \fq bona ukuthula kwabafowenu.\f* yini abafowenu, lokuthi uyaphila umhlambi, ungibuyisele ilizwi. Wasemthuma esuka esigodini iHebroni\x + 13.18; 35.27.\x* wasefika eShekema.
\p
\v 15 Indoda yamfica, ngoba khangela wayezula egangeni; indoda yasimbuza yathi: Udingani?
\v 16 Wasesithi: Ngidinga abafowethu; ake ungazise ukuthi balagise ngaphi.
\v 17 Indoda yasisithi: Basukile lapha, ngoba ngibezwile besithi: Asiye eDothani. UJosefa wasebalandela abafowabo, wabathola eDothani\x + 2 Kho. 6.13.\x*.
\v 18 Basebembona esekhatshana. Njalo engakasondeli kubo, bamenzela ugobe lokuthi bambulale.
\v 19 Bakhulumisana \add besithi\add*: Khangela, lo umphuphi\f + \fk umphuphi: \fl Heb. \fq inkosi yamaphupho.\f* uyeza;
\v 20 khathesi-ke, wozani simbulale, simphosele komunye wemigodi, besesisithi: Isilo esibi simdlile. Khona sizabona ukuthi amaphupho akhe azakuba yini.
\v 21 URubeni wasekuzwa, wamephula esandleni sabo, wathi: Asingatshayi impilo\x + 42.22.\x*.
\v 22 URubeni wasesithi kubo: Lingachithi igazi, mphoseleni kulumgodi osenkangala, lingeluleli isandla kuye; ukuze amkhulule esandleni sabo, ukuze ambuyisele kuyise\x + 37.29,30.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Kwasekusithi uJosefa esefikile kubafowabo, bamhlubula uJosefa isigqoko sakhe, isigqoko esilemibalabala\f + \fk esilemibalabala: \fl kumbe, \fq esiyiziqaziqa.\f*, ayesigqokile;
\v 24 basebemthatha, bamphosela emgodini; kodwa umgodi wawungelalutho, kungelamanzi kuwo.
\v 25 Basebehlala phansi ukudla isinkwa. Baphakamisa amehlo abo babona, khangela-ke, udwendwe lwamaIshmayeli luvela eGileyadi\x + 37.27,28,36; 39.1.\x*, lamakamela awo ethwele isinongo\x + 43.11.\x* lenhlaka lemure*\x + Jer. 8.22; 46.11. Hez. 27.17.\x*, ehamba ukukwehlisela eGibithe.
\v 26 UJuda wasesithi kubafowabo: Yinzuzo bani uba simbulala umfowethu, sifihle igazi lakhe\x + 37.20.\x*?
\v 27 Wozani, simthengise kumaIshmayeli\x + 1 Sam. 18.17.\x*, lesandla sethu kasingabi phezu kwakhe, ngoba umgumfowethu, inyama yethu\x + 29.14.\x*. Abafowabo basebelalela.
\v 28 Kwasekudlula amaMidiyani angabathengiselani\x + 25.2. Hlu. 6.3.\x*; basebemdonsa bamphakamisa uJosefa emgodini, bathengisa uJosefa kumaIshmayeli\x + 45.4. Hlab. 105.17. Seb. 7.9.\x* ngenhlamvu zesiliva ezingamatshumi amabili\x + 33.19; 20.16; 45.22. Hlu. 9.4; 16.5. 2 Kho. 5.5.\x*. Amusa-ke eGibithe.
\p
\v 29 Kwathi uRubeni ebuyela emgodini, khangela-ke, kakho uJosefa emgodini, wadabula izembatho zakhe\x + 37.34; 44.13.\x*.
\v 30 Wasebuyela kubafowabo wathi: Umfana kakho; mina-ke, ngizakuya ngaphi\x + 42.13,32,36; 44.31. Jer. 31.15. Lilo 5.7.\x*?
\v 31 Basebethatha isigqoko sikaJosefa, bahlaba izinyane lembuzi, bagxamuza isigqoko egazini\x + 37.23.\x*.
\v 32 Basebethumela isigqoko esilemibalabala, basisa kuyise, bathi: Lokhu sikuficile; akunanzelele ukuthi lesi yisigqoko sendodana yakho yini, loba hatshi\x + 38.25,26.\x*.
\v 33 Wasinanzelela wathi: Isigqoko sendodana yami! Isilo esibi simdlile, isibili udatshuliwe uJosefa\x + 37.20; 44.28.\x*.
\v 34 UJakobe wasedabula izembatho zakhe, wafaka ilembu lesaka ekhalweni lwakhe, wayililela indodana yakhe insuku ezinengi\x + 37.29. 2 Sam. 1.11.\x*.
\v 35 Njalo wonke amadodana akhe lamadodakazi akhe asukuma ukumduduza\x + 2 Sam. 12.17.\x*, kodwa wala ukududuzwa, wathi: Ngoba ngizakwehlela engcwabeni endodaneni yami ngilila\x + 42.38; 44.29,31.\x*. Uyise wamlilela njalo.
\v 36 AmaMidiyani\x + 25.2.\x* asemthengisa eGibithe kuPotifa, umphathi kaFaro, induna yabalindi.
